    <briefdescription>
<para>Simplified implementation of std::function_ref from C++26. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classMR_1_1FunctionRef" kindref="compound">FunctionRef</ref> can be used as a lightweight replacement for std::function in cases when:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>a callable exists (there&apos;s no equivalent to <computeroutput>std::function( nullptr )</computeroutput>)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>a callable is passed to a function that calls it immediately or passes to another function of the same kind </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
